  ║  • CSS custom properties for full theming                    ║
  ║                                                              ║
  ║  Key sections in this file:                                  ║
  ║    1. CSS – design tokens, layout, component styles          ║
  ║    2. SVG defs – shared gradients/filters                    ║
  ║    3. HTML – modals + main page structure                    ║
  ║    4. JS – audio, canvas, data, UI, animation                ║
  ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝
